          title: 'Is Local SEO Dead? What Actually Works in 2025',
          href: '/blog/local-seo-death',
          description: 'Learn which old local tactics stopped working and what stronger site structure looks like now.',
          image: '/images/local_seo_visibility_cover.png',
          imageAlt: 'Local SEO dashboard and search performance visuals',
          tag: 'SEO',
        },
        {
          title: 'Why Site Speed Still Affects Conversion',
          href: '/blog/site-speed-conversion',
          description: 'A practical look at why page speed and mobile experience still affect trust and lead flow.',
          image: '/images/speed_conversion_cover.png',
          imageAlt: 'Website analytics and conversion reporting',
          tag: 'Performance',
        },
      ]}
    />
  </article>
</Layout>

